{"ts": "2026-06-29T19:22:50", "level": "DEBUG", "logger": "trafilatura.main_extractor", "msg": "extra in p: p This is a complicated question. In one sense, yes, ChatGPT is safe, but users have to be smart about how they use it and children and teens should have adult supervision. After a recent lawsuit, OpenAI is adding even more guardrails to help users stay safe."}
